About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Show Synopsis : Four brave female police officers of Aminabad police station use their wittiness and emotional intelligence to tackle the various challenges they face at their work. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution are mostly unusual. Episode 4012: CCTV Shop Kaun Jayega?
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide arrives at the soda shop, only to discover it empty. When he questions everyone about their absence, they lie to him. Tapu Sena reveals Madhavi's scam ordeal, which Bhide was unaware of. Later, Jethalal and Iyer decide to pose as police officers to aid in apprehending the scammer at the CCTV shop.

Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Chaya, a 22-year-old female bank executive, lives with an elderly couple, Mr. and Mrs. Patil. Manohar Patil appears concerned about the conflict between his son Arvind and his daughter Komal. Manohar becomes concerned and calls Komal to notify her that her brother, Arvind, is on his way back from Canada. A burglary occurs later at the Patil residence. What is the source of the conflict between the siblings? What is Chaya's connection to the Patil family?

Without a major breakthrough within the first 48 hours of a crime, the chances of solving it are cut in half. snippet.title: Afghanistan Tour Of Sri Lanka | 2nd T20I | Highlights | 19th February 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-afghanistan-tour-of-sri-lanka-1700001384

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

Sri Lanka was put to bat first in the second T20I. The quickfire knocks from the openers, followed by a half-century from Sadeera Samarawickrama and the perfect finish to the innings by Angelo Mathews helped Sri Lanka reach 187 runs in the end. Afghanistan once again crumbled against the Sri Lankan bowlers as none of the batters could put up a proper fight. In the end, Afghanistan became all out for just 115 runs in 17 overs and Sri Lanka won the match by 72 runs.

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the First Single of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur.

Episode 4011: Scammer Ko Pakadna Hoga
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena and Popatlal are determined to conceal the truth about the gold chain from Bhide. Bhide says he went to the temple as Sonu got a new gold chain while Sonu feels bad for Bhide. Later, Tapu Sena and Popatlal devise a plan to apprehend the scammer. 

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Sunday Brunch With Sushmita Sen x Kamiya Jani | Aarya Antim Vaar | Ep 126 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App: https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

Our excitement knows no bounds as we host our dream guest, the iconic Sushmita Sen! Join us on this culinary and conversational journey as we explore Sushmita's love for Bengali maach, misti doi, and sondesh, while also uncovering her newfound passion for sushi. The air is filled with laughter and nostalgia as she fondly recalls the time she won Miss Universe, sharing entertaining stories and offering us a glimpse into her world. Brace yourselves for some etiquette tips straight from the graceful queen herself, adding a touch of elegance to our delightful brunch!

In this candid conversation, Sushmita also opens up about her experience reprising the iconic role in Aarya, the challenges faced, and the creative process behind the series' finale on Disney+hotstar

As we indulge in delectable sushi and dimsums, the conversation takes a meaningful turn towards the importance of health and self-love. Sushmita Sen, with her wisdom, guides us through the journey of prioritizing well-being. As the brunch unfolds, Sushmita's aura leaves us awestruck, a testament to the timeless charm and grace that defines her. 

Hit play now and immerse yourself in this unforgettable Sunday Brunch experience with Sushmita Sen. It's a rendezvous filled with laughter, delicious bites, heartwarming stories, and a touch of glamour, making it a brunch to remember. Don't miss the magic ‚Äì join us for an extraordinary time with the incredible Sushmita Sen! üåü

snippet.title: Aham ne Gopi ko kiya taiyaar! | Saath Nibhana Saathiya
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe *Star Plus* : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-LPIU24bQXVljUXivKEeRQ

About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ghaata Episode 44 [Eng Sub] - Adeel Chaudhry - Momina Iqbal - Mirza Zain Baig - 20th February 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Hamza and Rania are deeply in love, a fact known to the entire family. Yet, unbeknownst to them, their cousins Danish and Sana secretly harbor affection for the couple.
A tragic event turns Rania‚Äôs life upside down and has major consequences for her relationship with Hamza. Danish and Sana, motivated by their hidden malice, use the event to their advantage.
As the aftermath unfolds, the four cousins experience the hardships of love, betrayal, and suffering. Boundaries are crossed, and each of them battles personal demons in their pursuit of love.
Will Rania and Hamza manage to be together? Can Rania overcome the haunting consequences of the event, or will it define her life? Will Hamza stand by Rania during the most testing time of her life? And will Danish and Sana confess their feelings to Rania and Hamza, respectively?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Asad Jabal
Writer: Abida Manzoor Ahmed

Shiddat Episode 03 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - Digitally Presented by PEL - 19th February 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Shiddat Digitally Presented by PEL

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.title: Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire | Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
The guardians of nature. The protectors of humanity. The rise of a new empire. #GodzillaXKong - Only in Theaters March 29.

The epic battle continues! Legendary Pictures‚Äô cinematic Monsterverse follows up the explosive showdown of ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù with an all-new adventure that pits the almighty Kong and the fearsome Godzilla against a colossal undiscovered threat hidden within our world, challenging their very existence‚Äîand our own. ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire‚Äù delves further into the histories of these Titans and their origins, as well as the mysteries of Skull Island and beyond, while uncovering the mythic battle that helped forge these extraordinary beings and tied them to humankind forever.

Once again at the helm is director Adam Wingard. The film stars Rebecca Hall (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Night House‚Äù), Brian Tyree Henry (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúBullet Train‚Äù), Dan Stevens (‚ÄúGaslit,‚Äù ‚ÄúLegion,‚Äù ‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast‚Äù), Kaylee Hottle (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù), Alex Ferns (‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù ‚ÄúWrath of Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúChernobyl‚Äù) and Fala Chen (‚ÄúIrma Vep,‚Äù ‚ÄúShang Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings‚Äù).

The screenplay is by Terry Rossio (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù the ‚ÄúPirates of the Caribbean‚Äù series) and Simon Barrett (‚ÄúYou‚Äôre Next‚Äù) and Jeremy Slater (‚ÄúMoon Knight‚Äù), from a story by Rossio & Wingard & Barrett, based on the character ‚ÄúGodzilla‚Äù owned and created by TOHO Co., Ltd. The film is produced by Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric Mcleod, Thomas Tull and Brian Rogers. The executive producers are Wingard, Jen Conroy, Jay Ashenfelter, Yoshimitsu Banno, Kenji Okuhira.

Once again, Wingard is collaborating with director of photography Ben Seresin (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúWorld War Z‚Äù), production designer Tom Hammock (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúX,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Guest‚Äù), editor Josh Schaeffer (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMolly‚Äôs Game‚Äù), costume designer Emily Seresin (‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúTop of the Lake‚Äù). The composers are Tom Holkenborg (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù) and Antonio Di Iorio (additional music on ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù the ‚ÄúSonic the Hedgehog‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Adam Wingard, ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire.‚Äù It is slated for release nationwide only in theaters and IMAX on March 29, 2024 and beginning 27 March 2024 internationally, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures except in Japan, where the film will be distributed by Toho Co., Ltd and in mainland China, where it will be distributed by Legendary East.
